# Rule
- Always validate all input data and API parameters.
- Never trust data from external sources (user, plugins, third-party services).
- Use schemas, types, or validators (e.g., zod, pydantic, marshmallow).

# Examples
- ✅ `z.object({ email: z.string().email() })`
- ✅ `if not isinstance(user_id, int): raise ValueError()`
